\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"條友近排話報警拉手足<br />\n<br />\n其實佢衰過藍屍<br />\n<br />\n垃圾David<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b8b0d91e9c8cf2302e3bfebed2ae51188f579d","tid":2221150,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"又運動已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37932dfc5a41f21da28ed4deef8612f0e464f574","tid":2221150,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ced64328d306ec0270b5b3b98d45be2806b0829","tid":2221150,"uid":134474,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"咁樣其實佢哋想點？想David做乜，想香港人做乜<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁樣有少少怨婦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"#362<br />\nClaireXLeon<br />\n&bull;<br />\n10 分鐘前<br />\n可唔可以解釋下,點解唔可以各有各做,<br />\nDAVID 做左呢樣野, 佢地就做唔到佢地想做既野?<br />\nDavid的抗爭方法：<br />\n<br />\n唱歌（5201314）<br />\n叫口號（不包括違反国安法）<br />\n報警拉真手足<br />\n鳩企鳩坐做手勢<br />\n鳩搞活動搞鳩手足<br />\n寫信比林鄭同鄧炳強<br />\n要求同林鄭公開對話<br />\n喺周梓樂祭壇前玩可樂<br />\n嘗試搞個人崇拜搞埋大衛星級抗爭團隊<br />\n不斷同勇武手足割蓆 但自稱勇武<br />\n喺佢公海以民主自由之名 行獨裁之實<br />\n<br />\n仲有更多，歡迎投稿<br />\n<br />\n反正我從來都無當過佢係同路人，佢只係一舊喺現實生活本身比人睇唔起嘅垃圾，先需要借抗爭上位虛構自己嘅價值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋比意見佢改善活動方針 佢忠言逆耳<br />\n郁啲就當人分化撚/踢人出group<br />\n之前彥霖梓樂悼念會佢喺度撚狗嗌口號玩可樂<br />\n拖累到在場採訪緊嘅記者食599G<br />\n做旁聽師又喺度亂嗌口號搞到全村人一齊比狗圍住SS<br />\n然後冇人送到工程巴車<br />\n<br />\n先唔講佢搞嘅活動有冇成效或者影響力<br />\n剩係以上問題 加埋做錯嘢又唔認錯同道歉<br />\n比記者聲討但依然故我 態度囂張等問題<br />\n佢唔肯糾正錯誤嘅話 我真係不敢抬舉佢呢個人"},{"pid":"6e91089a8eea6e9ecebacf5c119b836e358ff2bf","tid":2221150,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1b8b0d91e9c8cf2302e3bfebed2ae51188f579d","tid":2221150,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"又運動已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"啫係要靠和你鳩維持？"},{"pid":"359eeff60dcba8babee21b389148381f6eb53903","tid":2221150,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1c5fe626afae24d42277966bce366492056d1d","tid":2221150,"uid":155781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e26fcc49696115676e41a5c4022a39278d4763c","tid":2221150,"uid":286897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"25ec7c45f49f80a6971e70a542bea9271dd20cd6","tid":2221150,"uid":155781,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"支持得David其實個人都有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"條友近排話報警拉手足<br />\n<br />\n其實佢衰過藍屍<br />\n<br />\n垃圾David<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:44:03.000Z","msg":"人哋要同柒婆對話㗎"},{"pid":"c6c096fa0a6ccde318b525506a18ee73ad26354b","tid":2221150,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"44383f23846be990b4a8979a4161d9010deefce2","tid":2221150,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"2d55d3d152aabd859e40490b42981455d2741c01","tid":2221150,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"支持赤巴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"thx"},{"pid":"7e8f65f07b373518e0ab035c0ca4a637e68d41b6","tid":2221150,"uid":320624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"david嘅夢想：談笑間，檣櫓灰飛煙滅<br />\n<br />\n咦等等，白卡仔都想做周瑜？人唔笑狗都吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3af4dd97694bd875b0e1dda85c7664a63a7b8f5","tid":2221150,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc